###########################
#  Initialization

DOCUMENT();

loadMacros(
"PGstandard.pl",
"MathObjects.pl",
"answerHints.pl",

"PGML.pl",
"PGcourse.pl",
"parserImplicitEquation.pl",
);

TEXT(beginproblem());

$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

###########################
#  Setup
Context("Numeric");

$a = random(5, 15);
$b = non_zero_random(-20,20);

$ans = ($b+$a)/2;

#For Solution
$rhs = $b+$a;

###########################
#  Main text

BEGIN_PGML

The difference of twice a number and [`[$a]`] is [`[$b]`] Find the number.

[`x = `] [_________________]{$ans}

END_PGML


############################
#  Solution

BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
Let x = a number

Twice a number: 2x

The difference of twice a number and [$a]:  [`2x - [$a]`]

We need to solve the equation:

[`2x - [$a] = [$b]`]

[`2x = [$rhs]`]

[`x = [$ans]`]


END_PGML_SOLUTION

COMMENT('MathObject version. Uses PGML.');

ENDDOCUMENT();